extendedInfo.description: "The Stars Above" allows any science fiction fan to join Captain Munoz and the crew of the UFS Discovery on their mission of discovery and adventure. Explore the federated systems, venture into uncharted territories and encounter strange and compelling life forms.Don't just interpret your dreams. Take control of your dreaming and live them. Get lucid. Get Dreamshuffle.This is the first dream expansion pack for Dreamshuffle and you'll need the free player (version 1.3) on your phone or tablet. Just search for Dreamshuffle in the market.
